def_cn: 美籍拉美移民；美籍拉美后裔
def_en: A Latino is a citizen of the United States who originally came from Latin America, or whose family originally came from Latin America.

def_cn: 美籍拉美人的；美籍拉美文化的
def_en: Latino means belonging or relating to Latino people or their culture.
